			<h2>Good neighbors</h2>
			<p>For deep, single-purpose operations&mdash;token audits, deprecation plans, codemods, stakeholder briefs&mdash;check out Murphy Trueman&rsquo;s excellent, MIT-licensed <a href="https://designsystemops.com/">Design System Ops</a> skill pack. This kit is the diagnostic frame; that&rsquo;s the tool chest. The station files cross-reference her skills where they&rsquo;re the right next move.</p>
